// Test ta.cmo (Chande Momentum Oscillator)
// 100 * (gains - losses) / (gains + losses) over the last N changes, which
// needs N+1 values. Close only ever rises here, so there are no losses.

// Bars: 6

// 5 gains of 1, no losses -> 100 * 5 / 5
cmo5 = ta.cmo(close, 5)
log.info(cmo5)

// Expected output:
// na
// na
// na
// na
// na
// 100
